videos.description: Ebuka Izundu gives a quick pass to Lonnie Walker at the top of the arc for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Miami's crisp ball movement leads to 3-pointer

videos.description: Gardner Webb's Liam O'Reilly drives to the rack and nails the tricky layup with the contact.
videos.headline: O'Reilly converts and-1 layup

videos.description: After getting a block on the defensive end, Dewan Huell takes a lob pass from Bruce Brown and throws down the dunk.
videos.headline: Miami's Huell throws down alley-oop after block

videos.description: Miami's Dewan Huell grabs the offensive rebound and goes up strong with the layup despite the contact.
videos.headline: Huell earns trip to the line after put back layup

videos.description: Chris Lykes pulls up from downtown and drills the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Miami's Lykes shows off the range

videos.description: After the great effort on the defensive end and grabbing the board, Dewan Huell runs back in transition and throws down the dunk.
videos.headline: Huell making presence felt on both ends of court
